      "title": "Health TUs on strike over transport issues",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Several health trade unions, including public health inspectors, are engaged in trade union action for the second day citing transportation difficulties to report to work.",
        "Public Health Inspectors, Midwives , ECG and EEG technicians, Association of the Medical Laboratory and Public Health Laboratory, Association of Dentists and the Association of Pharmacists are engaging in this trade union action."
      ],
